.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-MIGRATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-migrate \- apply pending schema migrations to the wallet database
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-migrate
.SH DESCRIPTION
Applies any pending incremental schema migrations to the wallet SQLite
database.
Safe to run repeatedly; already-applied migrations are skipped.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"migrations_applied":[N,...],"schema_version":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-stats (1)
